March has a tendency to bring a little madness. Whether you're filling out tax returns or a bracket, or simply giving away your energy to others, but sure to take a moment for yourself.

Even just one minute of gentle breathing (focusing on your inhale, a slight pause, and gently exhaling, repeat- while focusing on nothing but your breath) has been shown to lower blood pressure and help us shift from a state of sympathetic nervous operation (think “fight or flight”) to parasympathetic, which is our best state for feeling centered and calm.

Save this post and revisit it as many times as you need to take a pause and give yourself a little mindfulness in the madness.

In case you needed some inspiration during this weekend’s 20% off everything sale, we asked one of our founders, Gabby Reese to share her must-have Laird Superfood products.

Meet the team of amazing humans who make your Daily Ritual possible!

Most people are surprised to hear that we still pack every single order by hand, in our small town of Sisters, Oregon.

From our hands to your front door, our incredible fulfillment team members like Jackie, Emily, Tiffany, and Tanner work tirelessly to make sure that you are never without your favorite products. They take great care with each order, knowing that it’s going to you!

Although we’re growing and changing, we can promise that some things never will. We will always stay true to our values of putting people and the planet first, and making the best quality superfood products for you and your family.

From our Ohana to yours, every day. That’s the way we do it.

Do you know what's really in your coffee creamer? With so many plant-based alternatives these days it's hard to know what you're really getting... many with not actually all-natural "all-natural" advertising. Let us make your decision easy!

We make products that use real, fresh, plant-based ingredients. Mother nature made it perfectly and that's just how we like it. 

Our liquid creamer will take your coffee to the next level, with ingredients you can pronounce, and feel good about. We use the creamiest part of the coconut to achieve an irresistibly rich and luxurious texture. We’ve also added in a special blend of our favorite nourishing and energizing mushrooms; Chaga, Lion’s Mane, and Cordyceps.
